{"tid":416711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[官之兩個口] 教大外洩截圖 私隱署稱調查完結","createTime":"2017-09-28T03:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T09:23:27.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f5addc7170e317a4c410e1890fe9f9983d34881c","tid":416711,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:56:49.000Z","msg":"教育大學早前有閉路電視截圖外洩。私隱專員黃繼兒在公開活動表示，個人資料私隱專員公署在法律權力之內，已不需要再跟進，個案調查已完結。<br />\n<br />\n黃繼兒指出，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>公署只在個人資料當中作審查，教大已作補救措施，並已達效果</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n對於公署在事件上是否像「無牙老虎」無實質權力，黃繼兒表示，公署在每件事都有改善空間，未來會考慮不同的意見。"},{"pid":"178f3713b97ed59f09be2a206ad02515e3ef7850","tid":416711,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:57:13.000Z","msg":"官字兩個口，打撚錯自吞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119bb5b3df1d0aeed730447b041ad6a5f6147f3a","tid":416711,"uid":14346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:44:25.000Z","msg":"繼兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔怕生壞命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72d772047e75c7c9929ba23c0cef2a3013d74a1","tid":416711,"uid":76776,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:46:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"952aa3d48579c9c5acc1ced4d91459cf77083d80","tid":416711,"uid":7840,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:48:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"658dfd693f251fb6d62d33a6a89d304c0a0cbdf3","tid":416711,"uid":100626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:49:11.000Z","msg":"咁都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f90f24d404e9cad5bcb548bfdcbefe6ef9a2d8","ti